com.dukes.klein.parser.node

Class TerminalNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dukes.lang.parser.node.AbstractSyntaxNode
      • com.dukes.lang.parser.node.ExpressionNode
        • com.dukes.klein.parser.node.TerminalNode

  • public class TerminalNode
extends ExpressionNode
    A wrapper class for any String value. This allows classes to put Nodes on the stack without doing anything with these nodes. They are used to construct other nodes.
    Since:
    0.3.0
